title: Spaceship Pneumatic Airlock Door Sound Effect Pack 1-2
description: This sound effects pack is perfect for futuristic, sci-fi or other productions where pneumatic airlock door opening and closing sounds are required.
longDescription:
This sound effects pack is perfect for futuristic, sci-fi or other productions where pneumatic airlock door opening and closing sounds are required.


As a huge Sci-Fi fan, I've always loved the sounds of such movies whatever they were. So I couldn't leave pneumatic airlock doors out of my work. 


This sound effect collection is ideal for use in game software, applications.
technicalDetails:
Features:

  •  101 Pneumatic Airlock Door sound effect.
  •  For games, apps or productions where Airlock Door scenes appear. 

Number of Audio Waves: 101

Number of Audio Cues: 101

Sample rate / bit rate: 44,100 Hz / 16 bit / Stereo

Do Sound FX loop: No

Minutes of audio provided: 04min 17sec

Supported Development Platforms:

Windows: Yes

Mac: Yes
